# Keep text test data byte-identical across platforms. data_size (the on-disk
# file size) is asserted in the e2e snapshot, and git's autocrlf would otherwise
# check CSV/TSV out with \r\n on Windows, inflating their size and breaking the
# comparison. Binary formats (parquet, sqlite, xlsx, gpkg, sas7bdat) are
# auto-detected by git and left untouched.
*.csv text eol=lf
*.tsv text eol=lf
